squats_feedback.wrong: Knees caving in: This can stress the knees and reduce effectiveness
squats_feedback.correction: Focus on keeping knees aligned with your toes

squats_feedback.wrong: Knees caving in: This can stress the knees and reduce effectiveness.
squats_feedback.correction: Externally rotate your hips and keep your knees in line with your toes to reduce knee pressure.

squats_feedback.wrong: Inward knee collapse (valgus) during squats increases MCL stress.
squats_feedback.correction: Maintain proper knee alignment to distribute load evenly and reduce MCL pressure.
